fields.name: AdminUserEnabled
fields.description: The value that indicates whether the admin user is enabled.

fields.name: AnonymousPullEnabled
fields.description: Enables registry-wide pull from unauthenticated clients.

fields.name: CreationDate
fields.description: The creation date of the container registry in ISO8601 format.

fields.name: DataEndpointEnabled
fields.description: Enable a single data endpoint per region for serving data.

fields.name: DataEndpointHostNames
fields.description: List of host names that will serve data when dataEndpointEnabled is true.

fields.name: Encryption
fields.description: The encryption settings of container registry.

fields.name: LoginServer
fields.description: The URL that can be used to log into the container registry.

fields.name: NetworkRuleBypassOptions
fields.description: Whether to allow trusted Azure services to access a network restricted registry.

fields.name: NetworkRuleSet
fields.description: The network rule set for a container registry.

fields.name: Policies
fields.description: The policies for a container registry.

fields.name: PrivateEndpointConnections
fields.description: List of private endpoint connections for a container registry.

fields.name: ProvisioningState
fields.description: The provisioning state of the container registry at the time the operation was called.

fields.name: PublicNetworkAccess
fields.description: Whether or not public network access is allowed for the container registry.

fields.name: Status
fields.description: The status of the container registry at the time the operation was called.

fields.name: ZoneRedundancy
fields.description: Whether or not zone redundancy is enabled for this container registry
